{"title":"Working for HMPPS","public_updated_at":"2017-04-03T04:53:50Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We are currently recruiting prison officers and other operational roles. To find out more about the opportunities available visit <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.prisonandprobationjobs.gov.uk\">www.prisonandprobationjobs.gov.uk</a></p>\n\n<p>You can also search for a job at:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://justicejobs.tal.net/vx/lang-en-GB/mobile-0/appcentre-1/brand-2/candidate/jobboard/vacancy/3/adv/\">MoJ and HMPPS job search</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.civilservicejobs.service.gov.uk/csr/index.cgi\">civil service jobs</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>For those looking to apply for a role in HM Prison Service (HMPS), there are <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-prison-service/about/recruitment\">specific roles available</a>.</p>\n</div>","organisation":"37a2a3c3-ccd7-46b0-8b81-199a746a2768","tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":[],"topics":[]}},"routes":[{"path":"/government/organisations/her-majestys-prison-and-probation-service/about/recruitment","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"whitehall","rendering_app":"government-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"recruitment","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","first_published_at":"2017-04-03T04:53:50Z","base_path":"/government/organisations/her-majestys-prison-and-probation-service/about/recruitment","description":"Careers at Her Majesty’s Prison and Probation Service","content_id":"51d01503-4c12-4ba4-b58d-581aec6bbd5e","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"EA1213","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/her-majestys-prison-and-probation-service","base_path":"/government/organisations/her-majestys-prison-and-probation-service","content_id":"37a2a3c3-ccd7-46b0-8b81-199a746a2768","description":null,"document_type":"organisation